        # Markdown Heading
        This is a *Markdown* formatted paragraph.

        - Bullet point 1
        - Bullet point 2
    )";

    string htmlOutput = markdownToHTML(markdownInput);
    cout << htmlOutput << endl;

    return 0;
}
